data.description: Classic Charmer Just Outside the City! Excellent Flip or Reno!ALL REASONABLE OFFERS CONSIDERED!!! 13 minutes from the heart of Cleveland, and conveniently located near the ocoee region!Step back in time to this well built, hidden gem! Nestled on a tree lined quiet street, in a clean subdivision, this fixer upper is perfect for the growing family or the investor looking for a lot of house for the money. Sit and sip some sweet tea on the huge newer, covered front porch, complete with ramp for handicapped accessibility. Inside you'll find picture windows in the large great room with a mountain stone, wood burning fireplace. The front living room can easliy be converted back to a bedroom and a large eat in kitchen with unique built in cabinets is on the back. Washer/ dryer hookup is right next to the kitchen. Two good sized bedrooms and a recently remodeled bath upstairs, plus 2 bedrooms, bath and den and storage room in the full basement offer plenty of space.The roof, foundation, and hvac are in good condition.  Authentic hardwood floors underneath the carpet, a basement workshop, and one car garage make this home shine with potential! Situated on nearly a half-acre lot, add some TLC for a quick remodel to restore this large home to its bygone beauty. Being sold by heirs, AS IS. Call today for your showing. Due to estate, heirs request that closing be done through Burns, Henry & Kirksey, Cleveland, TN.
